{
  "slug": "microsoft-365",
  "name": "Microsoft 365 (Outlook & OneDrive)",
  "description": "Outlook email (envoi immédiat, brouillon), Outlook Calendar et OneDrive via Microsoft Graph API. OAuth 2.0 Bearer injecté par requête (X-OAuth-Token, multi-tenant Oriq).",
  "instructions": "Ce connecteur utilise Microsoft Graph API v1.0. L'authentification OAuth est gérée par Oriq : le token est injecté via X-OAuth-Token à chaque requête — aucune variable d'environnement à configurer manuellement.\n\nEndpoints Graph utilisés :\n- POST /v1.0/me/sendMail       (envoi email)\n- POST /v1.0/me/messages       (brouillon)\n- POST /v1.0/me/events         (événement calendrier)\n- PUT  /v1.0/me/drive/root:/{file_path}:/content  (fichier OneDrive)\n\nLes destinataires (toRecipients, ccRecipients, bccRecipients) et les participants (attendees) doivent être passés au format Graph : [{ emailAddress: { address: 'user@example.com' } }]. La conversion depuis les adresses simples est faite par le moteur Oriq (outlookRequestTransform).",
  "region": "intl",
  "category": "productivity",
  "icon": "microsoft",
  "docsUrl": "https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/overview",
  "requiredEnvVars": [],
  "connector": {
    "name": "Microsoft Graph (365)",
    "type": "REST",
    "baseUrl": "https://graph.microsoft.com",
    "authType": "BEARER_TOKEN",
    "authConfig": {
      "token": "{{MICROSOFT_GRAPH_ACCESS_TOKEN}}"
    }
  },
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "microsoft_outlook_send_now",
      "description": "Envoie immédiatement un email via Outlook. Demander confirmation explicite avant envoi.",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["subject", "to_recipients"],
        "properties": {
          "subject": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Objet du mail"
          },
          "to_recipients": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object" },
            "description": "Destinataires au format Graph : [{ emailAddress: { address: 'user@example.com' } }]"
          },
          "body_content": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Corps du message"
          },
          "body_content_type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["Text", "HTML"],
            "default": "Text"
          },
          "cc_recipients": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object" },
            "description": "Destinataires en copie au format Graph"
          },
          "save_to_sent_items": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true
          }
        }
      },
      "endpointMapping": {
        "path": "/v1.0/me/sendMail",
        "method": "POST",
        "bodyMapping": {
          "message": {
            "subject": "$subject",
            "body": {
              "contentType": "$body_content_type",
              "content": "$body_content"
            },
            "toRecipients": "$to_recipients",
            "ccRecipients": "$cc_recipients"
          },
          "saveToSentItems": true
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "microsoft_outlook_draft_create",
      "description": "Crée un brouillon email dans Outlook. Confirmation avant envoi.",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["subject", "to_recipients"],
        "properties": {
          "subject": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Objet du mail"
          },
          "to_recipients": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object" },
            "description": "Destinataires au format Graph : [{ emailAddress: { address: 'user@example.com' } }]"
          },
          "body_content": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Corps du message (texte ou HTML)"
          },
          "body_content_type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["Text", "HTML"],
            "default": "Text"
          },
          "cc_recipients": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object" },
            "description": "Destinataires en copie au format Graph"
          },
          "bcc_recipients": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object" },
            "description": "Destinataires en copie cachée au format Graph"
          }
        }
      },
      "endpointMapping": {
        "path": "/v1.0/me/messages",
        "method": "POST",
        "bodyMapping": {
          "subject": "$subject",
          "body": {
            "contentType": "$body_content_type",
            "content": "$body_content"
          },
          "toRecipients": "$to_recipients",
          "ccRecipients": "$cc_recipients",
          "bccRecipients": "$bcc_recipients"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "microsoft_outlook_event_create",
      "description": "Crée un événement dans le calendrier Outlook. Utiliser des dates ISO 8601 (ex: 2026-06-15T14:00:00).",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["subject", "start_datetime", "end_datetime"],
        "properties": {
          "subject": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Titre de l'événement"
          },
          "start_datetime": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Date/heure début ISO 8601 (ex: 2026-06-15T14:00:00)"
          },
          "end_datetime": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Date/heure fin ISO 8601"
          },
          "timezone": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "Europe/Paris",
            "description": "Fuseau horaire (ex: Europe/Paris)"
          },
          "attendees": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object" },
            "description": "Participants au format Graph : [{ emailAddress: { address: 'user@example.com' }, type: 'required' }]"
          },
          "body_content": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Description de l'événement"
          },
          "location": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Lieu de l'événement"
          }
        }
      },
      "endpointMapping": {
        "path": "/v1.0/me/events",
        "method": "POST",
        "bodyMapping": {
          "subject": "$subject",
          "start": {
            "dateTime": "$start_datetime",
            "timeZone": "$timezone"
          },
          "end": {
            "dateTime": "$end_datetime",
            "timeZone": "$timezone"
          },
          "body": {
            "contentType": "Text",
            "content": "$body_content"
          },
          "location": {
            "displayName": "$location"
          },
          "attendees": "$attendees"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "microsoft_onedrive_doc_create",
      "description": "Crée ou écrase un fichier dans OneDrive (Word, texte, etc.) via upload de contenu.",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["file_path"],
        "properties": {
          "file_path": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Chemin OneDrive du fichier (ex: Documents/rapport.docx)"
          },
          "content": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Contenu texte du fichier"
          },
          "content_type": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "text/plain",
            "description": "MIME type (text/plain, application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document)"
          }
        }
      },
      "endpointMapping": {
        "path": "/v1.0/me/drive/root:/{file_path}:/content",
        "method": "PUT",
        "bodyMapping": {
          "passthrough": true
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
